---
// src/components/EditorialFeatures.astro
---
<section class="features">
  <div class="feature-item">
    <span class="index">[01]</span> <strong>STRUCT_REFACTOR:</strong> Mengubah susunan kalimat habis-habisan biar lolos cek plagiasi, tanpa ngubah makna aslinya.
  </div>
  <div class="feature-item">
    <span class="index">[02]</span> <strong>CONTEXT_LOCK:</strong> Nggak cuma ganti kata, tapi nge-lock gaya bahasa dan nadanya biar hasilnya tetap enak dibaca.
  </div>
  <div class="feature-item">
    <span class="index">[03]</span> <strong>PIPELINE_SYNC:</strong> Proses berantai ID→NL→EN→ID yang jalan otomatis, dengan notifikasi real-time di tiap tahapannya.
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .features {
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 1rem auto 2rem;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 0.5rem;
    padding: 0;
    box-sizing: border-box;
  }

  .feature-item {
    background: transparent;
    color: #a3a3a3; /* Abu-abu redup khas Claude/DevTools */
    font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif;
    font-size: 0.85rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    font-weight: 400;
  }

  .index {
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    color: #737373;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    margin-right: 0.25rem;
  }

  .feature-item strong {
    display: inline-block;
    margin-right: 0.5rem;
    color: #e5e5e5; /* Putih netral terang */
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 500;
    letter-spacing: 0.02em;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .features {
      margin: 1rem auto 1.5rem;
      gap: 0.6rem;
    }

    .feature-item {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      line-height: 1.5;
    }
  }
</style>